Using "@chakra-ui/next-js": "^2.1.5" and "next": "13.5.6" I got the same error.

I solved this by removing the ColorModeScript tag. I set my initial color mode in the theme object.

`const theme = extendTheme({
  initialColorMode: 'light',
  useSystemColorMode: false,
});

<ChakraProvider theme={theme}>...`

